Syntax: cast 'magic missile'  <victim>
Syntax: cast 'wrath'          <victim>
Syntax: cast 'multiburst'     <victim>

These spells inflict damage on the victim.  The higher-level spells do
more damage.  COLOUR SPRAY is the weakest while MULTIBURST is the
strongest.  COLOUR SPRAY has a small chance of blinding its victim and
will decrease in the amount of given damage the more it is used.  Wrath
only damages evil mobs and will have a small chance of cursing them.
MULTIBURST, the strongest spell, releases a burst of magic missiles
whose level of damage depends on the caster's level.  Although the spell
can be weak at first, at high levels, it's the strongest of these spells.
~

