Hordes which our land have learn to deal with , are invaders of a
lost land that was once our neighboring nation .  From the words of
Crescent leaders before the one today , one message has taken a whole
new meaning : "we are not evil , merely different !!"  Crescent is
not evil , in there frame of thought ...  They just come to invade
and take over the whole region , because the think they can . 
Another way of thinking is : "Do you blame the wolf for killing the
deer?  Do not blame us for wanting the rule you !"  .  Crescent , it
