the centuries wore on, the human slaves gained more knowledge of
the planes and learned from their masters.  Eventually, they were 
powerful enough to revolt and liberate themselves.  By this time,
they had evolved into something higher than the human experience.
They had become something more.  Naming themselves "darnoks"
after a great leader of theirs, they returned to Thera in triumph.
