0 ALCHEMIST~
Alchemists are a jolly group of inventive magic users.  Though
lacking the sheer magical power of other mages, the alchemist is an
extremely useful friend to have. Their enhancing magics are greater
than any in the land.  Experienced Alchemists can perform several feats
including the long researched ability of transmogrification. Yes,
turning lead into gold. That is the foundation of Alchemy. Also, the
alchemistc can learn how to make wicked poison and empower weapons
and armor beyond the standard magical enhancement.  An Alchemist is
a useful class to have on your side.
