0 ASSASSIN~
Masters of the art of weaponless combat, these mysterious warriors have
recently become more common in the land. They strike quickly and
silently before fading into the shadows. Assassins are skilled in the
knowledge of nerve pressure, and can weaken their foes with a well placed
strike. Assassins learn the art of assassination, killing their foe
instantly and silently.  Due to their belief that touching the blades of
their opponent with their own blade is a loss of honor, Assassins cannot
parry with swords. Assassins are usually very anti-social and have little
in common with those "normal" citizens in Thera. To Assassins, even other
Assassins are not to be associated with. They are considered competition
and even a bit of a threat. Assassins are evil by nature and though most
are chaotic, some have found it more useful to obey the laws of the 
cities. After all, nobody can stay in the city forever and even Advisors
slip up.
