Stranger sees when looking at you, A PHYSICAL 
DESCRIPTION.  Not how you see yourself but how others do.
It should be described in this situation:
Awake, Standing, Facing the direction of the person looking at 
You, and from a close distance.  You should have a description
Containing at least 5 lines by the level 5.
