-Race
-Stature and Build (ex.  Slender, muscular, stocky, chubby, etc.), 
-Approximate height and weight
-Facial features (Nose, lips, mouth, cheeks, shape of face, etc.)
-Eyes (color, shape, size, emotion, etc.)
-Hair (color, length, texture, size, etc.)
-Demeanor <how your character carries him/herself>
   (aloof, graceful, threatening, carefree, wary, etc.)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
