-Actions of your own or others ("The first thing you notice is.."
or "You look at...")
-The word "you" ("Standing before you" is alright...Do not use
it as if you are forcing an action upon them.  Ex. "He picks up a 
rock and roars" or "You feel very afraid of this psychopath")
-Anything your wearing/clothing/equipment of any kind
-Titles (past or previous)
-Bragging of any kind (fastest, strongest, god-like)
-Greetings
