Standing before you is a male human.  He stands 
Around 11 hands tall and weighs approximately
45 stones. (Name) is stocky and has very well-defined 
muscles. His face is round with sharp cheek bones that 
bring out the jagged sockets hiding his eyes, dark blue 
eyes filled with mystery. His nose is large for the size
of his face while not being too obtrusive.  Just under it,
his mouth is surrounded by wrinkles that gives it the 
impression of a constant frown Jet black hair standing 
