0 DWARF~
{RGeneral:{B:  Dwarves are short, tough and mighty.  They are well known
for patronizing the bars and taverns of Thera, and tales of their drinking
skills are legendary.  They are also known for their ferocious fighting
and warfare skills.  Many an orc or goblinoid has trembled in fear at
