A long time ago, a young elf born in a noble and wealthy family
abandoned his town and life and vanished to the high mountains of Thera.
He left, with the disagreement of his father hoping to achieve something
no one has ever realized.
 
For years, he remained there meditating continuously...sitting on a
boulder sunrise after sunrise and sunset after sunset. His efforts 
were not in vain...after all the valiant hard work he had discovered
a new force, a new energy, a new magic which he calls potential energy,
Kii, or spiritual energy. This art of magic is hard to explain for it
still remains mysterious and highly varies from each individual. It is
created from within each creature and exists when they are born but few
are aware of its presence and even fewer know how to unleash it and
wield it.
 
The young elf had mastered this energy and had learned to wield it with
ease and skill. To master the force, a large amount of time and
concentration is required. Furthermore, one must have a clean heart and
soul in order to be able to master it. This young elf carried the name
of Lurai.
 
Years Later, an Elf named Legolas was taught the art of Kii by the
Master Lurai himself. 
 
The new disciple proves to be a great student that learns fast from 
the wise master. After several months of serious training, he has 
mastered alot from his tutor and was quite ready to depart on his own. 
 
But fate has its own ways of setting destiny, the next day, the Master
fell ill affected by great disease that isn
Legolas left to the greatest medicine brewers he knew and was given a
"remedy" that  proved to be useless on the grave disease the master had.
He had only one path open before him now....death.
 
On his death bed, the master calls his disciple and gives him his will... 
he had always wished to build a sanctuary, a stronghold,a kingdom for
all those pure of heart and mind that wish to devote themselves and
train theirselves into a new world of energy,a world of Kii, that no one
has ever  visioned or thought of. He asked his disciple to build his
dream: The kingdom of Lurai was born... 
 
As times goes by, kingdoms fall and kingdoms are born. Upon the will of
The Gods of Thera, the Order of Lurai as well as all the other kingdoms
of Thera feel and living of Thera  simply ceased to exist. Yet all was
not forgotten, the Tome written by Kii Master Legolas was preserved in
the Sanarian Library... 
The Tome of Ages 
 
Born in Elvander, an elf seeks to know more about the history of his
name, Legolas was his name. Upon his search he comes across with the
Tome of Ages. Guided by the God Salindor, Legolas discovered Kii. Taught
in dreams by  previous members of the Order, Legolas slowly learned to
wield Kii and as time went by, his mastering of the force grew... 
 
