Bountyhunting and hired PK is allowed on Fate. However, the following
guidelines must be followed.
 
(1) All requirements outlined in 'help pk' must be met by the person who
places the bounty. Effectively, they are initiating the PK, so all
onus is on them to have a good reason.
 
(2) Peforming a hired PK, and the PK itself, must not conflict with the
existing roleplay of the killer.
 
(3) The admins must be notified that a hired kill has taken place, since it
may be desireable to keep the deal secret. Therefore, both the killer and 
the person who hired him must write a note to 'admin' on board 3 out-lining
the deal. The bounty-placer must give a good PK reason in this note or he
will be punished for illegal PK.
