The totem heals all ogres in the room.  Ogres can only make one totem at a time,
but several ogres may place several totems in a room.
 
Darnok - "Phase"  SYNTAX: phase
Darnoks can harness their extraplanar powers and blink between the prime and ether
planes.  This makes them harder to hit.
 
Felar - "Distract"  SYNTAX: distract
